{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "🎯 RHINOMETRIC Observability Cockpit",
    "tags": ["rhinometric", "observability", "monitoring"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 38,
    "version": 0,
    "refresh": "10s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "type": "text",
        "title": "📡 Observability Stack Overview",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 3
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "# 🎯 RHINOMETRIC Observability Cockpit\n\n**Real-time monitoring of your entire observability stack**\n\n| Component | Status | Endpoint |\n|-----------|--------|----------|\n| 🔥 **Prometheus** | Metrics Collection | http://localhost:9090 |\n| 📊 **Grafana** | Visualization | http://localhost:80 |\n| 🔍 **Loki** | Log Aggregation | http://localhost:3100 |\n| 🔗 **Tempo** | Distributed Tracing | http://localhost:3200 |\n| 📈 **cAdvisor** | Container Metrics | http://localhost:8080 |\n| ⚡ **Promtail** | Log Shipper | Internal |\n\n---"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "🔥 Prometheus Metrics",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 3,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Prometheus Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"prometheus\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Active Targets",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 4,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "count(up == 1)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Samples Ingested/s",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 8,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(prometheus_tsdb_head_samples_appended_total[5m])",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "ops",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 10000,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 5000, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 8000, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "TSDB Size",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "prometheus_tsdb_storage_blocks_bytes / 1024 / 1024",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "min": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 500, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 1000, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Query Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 16,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(prometheus_http_requests_total{handler=\"/api/v1/query\"}[5m])",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Scrape Duration",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 20,
          "y": 4,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(scrape_duration_seconds)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s",
            "decimals": 3,
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 0.5, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Metric Ingestion Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(prometheus_tsdb_head_samples_appended_total[5m])",
            "legendFormat": "Samples/s",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "ops",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Active Series",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "prometheus_tsdb_head_series",
            "legendFormat": "Series",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "🔍 Loki Logs",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 16,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 12,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Loki Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 17,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"loki\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 13,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Log Ingestion Rate",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 4,
          "y": 17,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(loki_ingester_lines_received_total[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "logs/s",
            "min": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 1000, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 5000, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 14,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Active Streams",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 9,
          "y": 17,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(loki_ingester_streams)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 15,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Query Duration",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 14,
          "y": 17,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loki_request_duration_seconds_bucket{route=\"/loki/api/v1/query_range\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 5,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 2, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 4, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 16,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Bytes Processed",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 19,
          "y": 17,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(loki_ingester_bytes_received_total[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "Bps",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 17,
        "type": "logs",
        "title": "Recent Platform Logs",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 21,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 10
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{job=\"rhinometric\"} |= ``",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": true,
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 18,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "🔗 Tempo Traces",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 31,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 19,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Tempo Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 32,
          "w": 4,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"tempo\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 20,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Spans Ingested/s",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 4,
          "y": 32,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(tempo_ingester_spans_received_total[5m]))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "spans/s",
            "min": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 500, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 1000, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 21,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Active Traces",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 9,
          "y": 32,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(tempo_ingester_traces_created_total)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 22,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Query Latency (p99)",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 14,
          "y": 32,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(tempo_request_duration_seconds_bucket{route=\"/api/traces/:traceID\"}[5m])) by (le))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "s",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 2,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 1.5, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 23,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Storage Size",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 19,
          "y": 32,
          "w": 5,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(tempo_ingester_bytes_received_total) / 1024 / 1024",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 24,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Span Ingestion Over Time",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 36,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(tempo_ingester_spans_received_total[5m])) by (job)",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "spans/s",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 25,
        "type": "row",
        "title": "📈 cAdvisor Container Metrics",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 44,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 1
        },
        "collapsed": false
      },
      {
        "id": 26,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "cAdvisor Status",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 45,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"cadvisor\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 27,
        "type": "stat",
        "title": "Monitored Containers",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 6,
          "y": 45,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "count(count by (name) (container_last_seen{name=~\"rhinometric-.*\"}))",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 28,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Total CPU Usage",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 45,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{name=~\"rhinometric-.*\"}[5m])) * 100",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 400,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 200, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 300, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 29,
        "type": "gauge",
        "title": "Total Memory Usage",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 18,
          "y": 45,
          "w": 6,
          "h": 4
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(container_memory_usage_bytes{name=~\"rhinometric-.*\"}) / 1024 / 1024",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "min": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 2000, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 4000, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 30,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "CPU Usage by Container",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 49,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{name=~\"rhinometric-.*\"}[5m]) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 31,
        "type": "timeseries",
        "title": "Memory Usage by Container",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 49,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "container_memory_usage_bytes{name=~\"rhinometric-.*\"} / 1024 / 1024",
            "legendFormat": "{{name}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "folderId": 0,
  "overwrite": true
}
